1
00:01:31,970 --> 00:01:36,670
[Eternal Brotherhood 2]

2
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:44,820
[Episode 17]

3
00:01:51,650 --> 00:01:52,110
My Lord,

4
00:01:52,509 --> 00:01:54,690
all our provisions have been taken away.

5
00:01:54,690 --> 00:01:55,310
More importantly...

6
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,400
More importantly,

7
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:58,200
we don't even know where

8
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,660
the enemy's main force is.

9
00:02:02,620 --> 00:02:03,110
My Lord,

10
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:06,600
we must beg forgiveness
from the Divine Emperor.

11
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,560
First, we concealed

12
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,720
the failure of the attack
on the sacred temple,

13
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:11,820
then the Yuanzhou
Alliance Army's rebellion,

14
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:13,800
followed by the King of Light's uprising.

15
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,660
Now we've lost three more cities.

16
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:17,870
We haven't mentioned any of this

17
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,600
to the Divine Emperor, My Lord.

18
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,050
If we report the truth,

19
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,320
do you know what awaits us?

20
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,370
In the battle of Moon Bay,

21
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:45,300
I killed countless enemies,

22
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,360
which led to my current position.

23
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,150
If we surrender now,

24
00:02:57,329 --> 00:02:59,590
all our previous efforts will be in vain.

25
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,710
So we must fight on

26
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,630
until we win.

27
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:10,150
My Lord, a troop is approaching us.

28
00:03:10,570 --> 00:03:11,520
From which direction?

29
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,650
From the southwest.

30
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:14,520
From the southwest?

31
00:03:15,140 --> 00:03:18,140
There shouldn't be
any enemy troops in the southwest.

32
00:03:24,870 --> 00:03:26,340
It's not the enemy coming.

33
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,280
Then who is it?

34
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,530
Chief, we just received news

35
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,030
that Ling Buxu of the North Clan

36
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:37,430
is leading his troops
towards Lu Di's camp.

37
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,079
Ling Buxu has been stationed

38
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:41,079
in the Southwest Camp east of Wayun,

39
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,990
supporting each other with Lu Di.

40
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,720
If their forces join together,

41
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:47,100
I'm afraid we won't be able to handle it.

42
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,700
Then we should strike first!

43
00:03:49,350 --> 00:03:52,660
No, with Ling Buxu's arrival,

44
00:03:53,250 --> 00:03:55,250
I actually feel a bit sorry for Lu Di.

45
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:59,250
Chief, have you lost
your mind from all the fighting?

46
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,400
There's no reason
to feel sorry for your enemy.

47
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,000
The provisions for the Southwest Camp

48
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,730
have always been
supplied from two sources.

49
00:04:04,730 --> 00:04:07,320
First, supplies are transported
from within the North Clan territory,

50
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,530
But the route is long.

51
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:09,880
It's very troublesome.

52
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,240
So the other main source

53
00:04:12,370 --> 00:04:15,150
is Lu Di's grain collection
from various parts of Yuanzhou.

54
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,269
As we all know,

55
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,000
Lu Di doesn't have time now

56
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,510
to transport grain for the Southwest Camp.

57
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:21,680
A couple of days ago, near Talin,

58
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:24,740
we intercepted
a North Clan squad transporting grain.

59
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,780
Now it seems that this squad

60
00:04:26,810 --> 00:04:29,360
must have been the supply team
heading to the Southwest Camp.

61
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,190
That's right.

62
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:33,240
So, Ling Buxu's trip

63
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,450
not for reinforcement,

64
00:04:35,590 --> 00:04:37,950
but to ask for punishment.

65
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,870
If that's the case,

66
00:04:41,230 --> 00:04:43,700
let's say a prayer for Lu Di?

67
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:52,600
You've been beaten
so badly by the Yuanzhou people

68
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,000
that you even lost Talin.

69
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,750
[Ling Buxu]

70
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:56,600
The King of Light's military strategy
is indeed extraordinary.

71
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,860
Those are all excuses.

72
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,830
The North Clan was routed
by the people of Yuanzhou.

73
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,070
It's unheard of.

74
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:08,540
General, how do you plan
to explain this to the Divine Emperor?

75
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,480
Explain what?

76
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,720
The defeat.

77
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,070
Am I defeated?

78
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,310
Arent' you?

79
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,080
Nonsense.

80
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:20,160
As if those Yuanzhou scum could defeat me.

81
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,270
They're just a bunch of farming slaves.

82
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:23,010
A pack of dogs.

83
00:05:23,010 --> 00:05:23,810
Is that so?

84
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:28,830
It seems you've been bitten
quite badly by these dogs.

85
00:05:32,190 --> 00:05:33,720
Please calm down, My Lords.

86
00:05:33,730 --> 00:05:35,760
We should unite
against our common enemy now.

87
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,500
We can't let outsiders
take advantage of this situation.

88
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,030
My Lords.

89
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,190
Please, My Lord.

90
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:47,520
Here, My Lord.

91
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:58,560
I was just careless
for a moment and fell into their trap.

92
00:05:58,970 --> 00:06:00,140
Once I regroup,

93
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,160
I'll definitely twist off
the King of Light's head

94
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,420
and use it as a wine jug.

95
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,000
Good.

96
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:08,420
Then I'll be waiting
for news of your victory, General.

97
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:11,230
However, for now,
I need to send a messenger

98
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,160
to thoroughly investigate
your battle losses

99
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,480
and verify each detail

100
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:17,600
so I can report truthfully
to the Divine Emperor.

101
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,000
General.

102
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:23,270
Take care of yourself.

103
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,680
Farewell.

104
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,950
Who does this Ling Buxu think he is,

105
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:42,680
daring to speak to me like that?

106
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,310
If it weren't for
the Divine Emperor's sake,

107
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:48,570
I would have already ripped his head off.

108
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:50,430
My Lord, please calm down first.

109
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:53,270
The most important thing for us now

110
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:55,730
is to focus on
how to defeat the King of Light.

111
00:06:56,850 --> 00:06:59,159
General Ling has left a messenger.

112
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,070
Soon, the news of our defeat

113
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,930
will be sent back to Sairong City.

114
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:06,090
If the Divine Emperor learns
that we have no more victories,

115
00:07:06,090 --> 00:07:08,090
we'll surely feel worse than death.

116
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,630
Where are your provisions located?

117
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,370
Speak quickly.

118
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,120
My Lord.

119
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,390
You may go.

120
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:24,790
My Lord, General Ling has ordered me

121
00:07:24,790 --> 00:07:27,610
to come and inventory
your remaining provisions and supplies,

122
00:07:27,610 --> 00:07:29,050
as well as assess the battle losses.

123
00:07:29,050 --> 00:07:31,260
I kindly request your cooperation
in providing this information.

124
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:34,380
How do you plan
to report this to the Divine Emperor?

125
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,909
Naturally, I will report truthfully.

126
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,520
General Ling!

127
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,770
Leep an eye on Ling Buxu.

128
00:07:58,409 --> 00:07:59,970
Kill everyone

129
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:02,130
who was sent to the Divine Castle.

130
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,280
Yes.

131
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:08,750
If we lose again this time,

132
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,970
I'll have no place left to stand.

133
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:16,190
So the King of Light must die.

134
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:21,350
Candied hawthorns for sale!

135
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,310
Young lady, would you like a skewer?

136
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:24,970
Ma'am,

137
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:26,950
what did you make these candied haws?

138
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,120
You jest, young lady.

139
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,120
Of course, candied hawthorns are made with

140
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,750
hawthorns and malt sugar.

141
00:08:31,290 --> 00:08:32,150
I see.

142
00:08:32,770 --> 00:08:34,440
Malt sugar as sweet as you.

143
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:38,270
So, how's business?

144
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:40,450
If you're not buying,
don't disturb their business.

145
00:08:40,450 --> 00:08:41,840
You're the one disturbing.

146
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,750
It's alright.

147
00:08:43,010 --> 00:08:44,630
Business has been good these days.

148
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:46,000
I was just about to hire some help

149
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,980
to make candied hawthorns with me.

150
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:47,580
Is that so?

151
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:50,930
Lord Xiu will be pleased to hear this.

152
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:53,080
-Next time.
-Bye.

153
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,120
Since when did Xiu

154
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,510
develop a habit
of eating candied hawthorns?

155
00:08:58,510 --> 00:08:59,840
How long has it been since you've seen

156
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,650
a candied hawthorn vendor in Yuanzhou?

157
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:02,530
Look at it now.

158
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:05,740
Yuanzhou used to be poor.

159
00:09:05,770 --> 00:09:06,940
Everything was waiting to be rebuilt.

160
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:08,670
People couldn't even afford to eat.

161
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,800
They only hoped to harvest more grain.

162
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:15,030
But now, after the revival of business,

163
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:18,030
besides necessities,
people can even afford sweets.

164
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:20,720
It shows that the people of Yuanzhou
are becoming more prosperous,

165
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,180
with higher aspirations.

166
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,860
This is all thanks to Lord Xiu's efforts.

167
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,880
Do you know what Yuanzhou lacks now?

168
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:27,920
What?

169
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:29,660
Chunfeng Garden.

170
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,080
You...

171
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,500
Stop right there!

172
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,790
I'm back.

173
00:09:42,010 --> 00:09:43,010
What is it?

174
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:44,370
It looks heavy.

175
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:46,280
Did you go shopping?

176
00:09:46,430 --> 00:09:47,010
No.

177
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:48,860
These are from the people of Yuanzhou.

178
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:51,390
They said it's stationery
for our office use.

179
00:09:51,710 --> 00:09:54,480
It seems the commerce
in Bulu Village is recovering well.

180
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,910
It's not just Bulu Village.

181
00:09:55,910 --> 00:09:56,790
The other administrative areas

182
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:58,920
have also gradually resumed farming.

183
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,640
According to Chief's strategy,

184
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,310
to recuperate.

185
00:10:02,610 --> 00:10:04,210
our taxes are extremely low.

186
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,270
The people now

187
00:10:05,270 --> 00:10:07,910
are highly motivated to farm.

188
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,370
Then how do we
manage our military expenses?

189
00:10:12,370 --> 00:10:14,230
We don't need military expenses.

190
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:16,590
We only need provisions and weapons,

191
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:19,370
and funds
for troop movement and relocation.

192
00:10:20,050 --> 00:10:21,560
Based on the current tax revenue,

193
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,720
we have enough.

194
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:24,300
We even have a surplus.

195
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,710
I didn't expect this.

196
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:30,230
You have the talent
to be a Chief Remonstrator.

197
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:39,240
Luo Jie,

198
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:42,200
have the North Clan soldiers
we captured earlier

199
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,200
help with mining.

200
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,390
Before Lu Di initiates negotiations,

201
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:48,600
they might as well be put to work.

202
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,330
Understood.

203
00:10:51,630 --> 00:10:53,230
Will Lu Di negotiate with us?

204
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,060
It's only a matter of time.

205
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:59,870
Besides, mining
is very beneficial for us now.

206
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:02,200
In fact, I've already
sent scouts from the Xiu Battalion

207
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,800
west of Wayun
to establish trade connections.

208
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,750
Establish trade?

209
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:07,360
Chief,

210
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:10,390
you want to engage
in border trade with Zichuan?

211
00:11:11,510 --> 00:11:14,670
The regulations
for goods circulation within Zichuan

212
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,480
have resulted in

213
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,320
very difficult circulation
of goods within Zichuan.

214
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:21,320
Meanwhile, Yuanzhou
is rich in mineral resources.

215
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,000
Some types of minerals

216
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:25,750
are very scarce

217
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,360
resources within Zichuan.

218
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,240
So this is our advantage.

219
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:31,870
However, we can
only trade with gold coins.

220
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:33,600
But we don't lack anything now,

221
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,320
why bother doing this?

222
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:38,670
If we truly want the people of Yuanzhou

223
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,200
to have a better life,

224
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,630
what we're doing now is far from enough.

225
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,370
In the battle against Lu Di,

226
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,770
we've always been afraid to face head-on.

227
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:51,000
The real reason

228
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,390
is that Yuanzhou's infrastructure

229
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:55,550
is far inferior to the North Clan's.

230
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:58,150
Not to mention
compared to the Zichuan family

231
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,570
and the Liufeng family.

232
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:02,430
Agricultural
and construction technologies,

233
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:05,180
schools, armories, and hospitals...

234
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,240
All these things beneficial to

235
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,270
the development of Yuanzhou's people,

236
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:12,360
we need to go back
to Zichuan to learn about them

237
00:12:12,550 --> 00:12:14,210
in order to develop Yuanzhou.

238
00:12:14,330 --> 00:12:16,730
This is our true purpose and mission.

239
00:12:17,690 --> 00:12:20,090
Chief, regarding this matter,

240
00:12:21,090 --> 00:12:23,330
who do you think would be suitable?

241
00:12:47,830 --> 00:12:50,000
My stomach hurts. It hurts so bad.

242
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:52,690
Chief.

243
00:12:52,890 --> 00:12:54,470
Although I know the food
in the Imperial Capital is delicious,

244
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:55,820
the beds are comfortable,
and the wine is good,

245
00:12:55,820 --> 00:12:57,150
not to mention Chunfeng Garden...

246
00:12:57,150 --> 00:12:57,780
Chief,

247
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:59,690
this time you can't
go back no matter what.

248
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:02,420
We need to resolve
Lu Di's matter first, at least.

249
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:03,610
You guys...

250
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,390
Alright.

251
00:13:07,930 --> 00:13:08,670
Then let's at least

252
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:10,030
solve the lunch problem first.

253
00:13:10,030 --> 00:13:10,440
Okay.

254
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,520
The noodles are here.

255
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:16,800
Thank you, sir.

256
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:21,140
Sir, we didn't order this.

257
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,410
It's on the house.
Enjoy your meal.

258
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,320
Thank you.

259
00:13:24,890 --> 00:13:27,090
Chief, do you have a stake in this place?

260
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:35,510
Why does the taste
of these noodles seem so familiar?

261
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:37,440
The taste of the Imperial Capital.

262
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:40,050
It's my exclusive recipe

263
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,680
that I gave to this owner.

264
00:13:41,850 --> 00:13:43,840
It tastes exactly the same
as the noodle stand

265
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,010
at the city gate of the Imperial Capital.

266
00:13:45,010 --> 00:13:46,140
I suddenly realized

267
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:49,360
that I'm quite accomplished
in culinary arts as well.

268
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,450
No wonder.

269
00:13:51,290 --> 00:13:52,910
The owner of the noodle stand
in the Imperial Capital

270
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,580
never adds meat for free.

271
00:13:58,770 --> 00:13:59,700
Hurry up and eat.

272
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,970
Someone get me another bottle.

273
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:21,420
How many dishes
did you have to get this drunk?

274
00:14:24,190 --> 00:14:24,920
Let's drink.

275
00:14:37,700 --> 00:14:40,030
The Chief must be especially happy today.

